---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FAQ | FreeOnlyFanz"
  description="Common questions about FreeOnlyFanz, curated picks, and outbound links."
  canonicalPath="/faq/"
>
  <article class="info-page container">
    <header class="info-page-header">
      <p class="info-eyebrow">FAQ</p>
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="info-page-body">
      <h2>Is FreeOnlyFanz affiliated with a creator platform?</h2>
      <p>No. We are an independent directory. Platform names you see on destination sites belong to those sites.</p>

      <h2>Do you host creator content?</h2>
      <p>No. We list links and short browsing context. Content lives on third-party pages when you click through.</p>

      <h2>Why do picks change?</h2>
      <p>We rotate shelves and categories over time. Nothing here is a promise that a specific page stays listed forever.</p>

      <h2>Are links sponsored?</h2>
      <p>Some may be. Sponsored or affiliate links may earn us a commission. We still aim to keep the directory useful, not
        spammy.</p>

      <h2>Who can use this site?</h2>
      <p>Adults only (18+). If you are not of legal age in your area, do not use FreeOnlyFanz.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
